May 05, 1960 - Aldo Ray and Wife Arrive In London.Hollywood Tough Guy And His English Bride: Hollywood ''Tough Guy'' Aldo Ray and his 21 year of wife - English Girl Johanna Bennett arrived at London Airport this morning - for the premiere of his newest film ''The Day They Robbed the Bank of England''. Johanna's fathers Major General Roland Bennett - Physician at the Royal Chelsea Hospital. The couple were married in California in March. Photo Show Aldo Ray and his wife on arrival at London Airport this morning.
